de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.core.measurement.order

Interface MeasurementEventVisitor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMeasurementEventVisitor

    public interface MeasurementEventVisitor
    A visitor for MeasurementEvents useful to iterate over a sequence of different such events. Implements the well known visitor pattern.
